{"tid":2385993,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廚具店男東主向途人揮刀判囚3個月 求情指社會事件影響生意 官籲放下仇恨","createTime":"2021-01-29T10:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T11:53:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"22ac4a41f07ccbeb7a1c44483fa5c3d036eebbcd","tid":2385993,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F5095&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1wzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=465908aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5095</a><br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】46歲廚具店男東主前年10月初深夜到屯門一連鎖餐廳內外接連向食客及途人揮刀，向青年高叫「造成唔方便」後遭追打致暈倒，回家後凌晨於住所被捕。男東主今午在屯門裁判法院承認1項在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，求情指公司因社會事件生意不佳，個人熱心公益，事件中已受嚴重襲擊，飽受懲罰。裁判官水佳麗稱對揮刀自衛辯解感到不解，期望被告頓悟，放下仇恨，「必須要謹守自己，唔放任自己行為」，遂判處被告監禁3個月。<br />\n<br />\n被告黎浩然被控2019年10月5日於屯門鄉事會路117至157號的康麗花園外的公眾地方，管有1把刀。（全文）<br />\n<br />\n#20210129新聞 #非手足"},{"pid":"59c1b88ef60153dba90931e025245f32fa043678","tid":2385993,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:12:09.000Z","msg":"藍屍都有中國人之分，中國人就咩事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460922748281490c01e2e3ef12e0a34a47dad646","tid":2385993,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:13:21.000Z","msg":"唔洗阻嚇嘅？ 如果佢斬到人 會引起大眾恐慌同混亂 若引起人踩人 後果不堪設想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b479de2ed303cdae7805bee8a5664942d8abe3","tid":2385993,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"打傷人先3個月，藏有laser pointer就8個月"},{"pid":"b7083e9d2d123692341d295de8f1e3f07c1af9e9","tid":2385993,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"Ig出個post 都9個月"},{"pid":"665f476959d3e37ab6d7b7b83a1e303a2757b3fb","tid":2385993,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做咩唔係熱愛社會既？"},{"pid":"100f6e7d363cfb1178155ea6de08b8b56ff10eb5","tid":2385993,"uid":388108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"460922748281490c01e2e3ef12e0a34a47dad646","tid":2385993,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:13:21.000Z","msg":"唔洗阻嚇嘅？ 如果佢斬到人 會引起大眾恐慌同混亂 若引起人踩人 後果不堪設想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"攞刀斬人 放下仇恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n羅索帶 後果不堪設想<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f38446f95093b2153680f941798a8995507dbc6","tid":2385993,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:15:49.000Z","msg":"向青年高叫「造成唔方便」後遭追打致暈倒，回家後凌晨於住所被捕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97092629cca78c50a9117d65c454a5f95be2a1bc","tid":2385993,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:16:49.000Z","msg":"宜家武肺事件係咪要出黎斬人?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6caae4415ca6075f359d1876d570f7bd930c40a1","tid":2385993,"uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:22:53.000Z","msg":"屯門另一庭管有觀塘星筆就5隻"},{"pid":"93d4290cfaf2fde4a05f2d3640669d0058f51b63","tid":2385993,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屯門另一庭管有觀星筆就5隻</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ac224a43684f547